msgctxt "#32093"
msgid "HDR tone mapping for previews"
msgstr "HDR tone mapping for previews"

msgctxt "#32094"
msgid "Tone-map HDR and Dolby Vision sources to SDR when generating trickplay JPEGs so colours match normal playback (similar to Jellyfin). Only applies to HDR/DV files; SDR generation is unchanged. Significantly slower on 4K HEVC — often several times longer per file — and requires ffmpeg tonemap support. Leave off if Jellyfin already generates sidecars or generation time matters."
msgstr "Tone-map HDR and Dolby Vision sources to SDR when generating trickplay JPEGs so colours match normal playback (similar to Jellyfin). Only applies to HDR/DV files; SDR generation is unchanged. Significantly slower on 4K HEVC — often several times longer per file — and requires ffmpeg tonemap support. Leave off if Jellyfin already generates sidecars or generation time matters."

msgctxt "#32095"
msgid "HDR dovi_tool fallback"
msgstr "HDR dovi_tool fallback"

msgctxt "#32096"
msgid "When HDR tone mapping is on, run dovi_tool on the first seconds of HEVC if ffprobe finds no HDR signals. Slower; place dovi_tool in generator ffmpeg bin/ (same folder as HDR ffmpeg) or on PATH. Use for stubborn Dolby Vision remuxes. Skipped for VFS stream paths. With fallback on, Run can offer to download dovi_tool there."
msgstr "When HDR tone mapping is on, run dovi_tool on the first seconds of HEVC if ffprobe finds no HDR signals. Slower; place dovi_tool in generator ffmpeg bin/ (same folder as HDR ffmpeg) or on PATH. Use for stubborn Dolby Vision remuxes. Skipped for VFS stream paths. With fallback on, Run can offer to download dovi_tool there."

msgctxt "#32097"
msgid "Generator ffmpeg path"
msgstr "Generator ffmpeg path"

msgctxt "#32098"
msgid "Optional folder or ffmpeg binary for trickplay generation (needs zscale or libplacebo for HDR tone mapping). Preview cropping uses Pillow separately. Leave empty to use /storage/.kodi/system/ffmpeg/ on Linux Kodi, or addon_data/service.trickplay/system/ffmpeg/ on Windows, when present; otherwise PATH. Use Install preview tools when the generator or HDR tone mapping is enabled, or batch Run when generating."
msgstr "Optional folder or ffmpeg binary for trickplay generation (needs zscale or libplacebo for HDR tone mapping). Preview cropping uses Pillow separately. Leave empty to use /storage/.kodi/system/ffmpeg/ on Linux Kodi, or addon_data/service.trickplay/system/ffmpeg/ on Windows, when present; otherwise PATH. Use Install preview tools when the generator or HDR tone mapping is enabled, or batch Run when generating."

msgctxt "#32099"
msgid "HDR tone mapping needs a capable ffmpeg build. Download and install now?\n\nLinux: BtbN gpl-8.1 (zscale). Windows: Gyan full build (zscale + libplacebo for Dolby Vision via Vulkan).\n\nOn devices without Vulkan (e.g. CoreELEC), Profile 5 Dolby Vision uses dovi_tool instead of libplacebo.\n\nInstall location: %s"
msgstr "HDR tone mapping needs a capable ffmpeg build. Download and install now?\n\nLinux: BtbN gpl-8.1 (zscale). Windows: Gyan full build (zscale + libplacebo for Dolby Vision via Vulkan).\n\nOn devices without Vulkan (e.g. CoreELEC), Profile 5 Dolby Vision uses dovi_tool instead of libplacebo.\n\nInstall location: %s"

