msgctxt "#32114"
msgid "Skip Dolby Vision Profile 5"
msgstr "Skip Dolby Vision Profile 5"

msgctxt "#32115"
msgid "When enabled, batch generation skips web-style Dolby Vision Profile 5 files (e.g. .DV. releases). Profile 5 needs a full dovi_tool convert before tonemapping — often hours plus ~1× video size temp space on devices like CoreELEC. Use a desktop with Vulkan or leave this off to process them."
msgstr "When enabled, batch generation skips web-style Dolby Vision Profile 5 files (e.g. .DV. releases). Profile 5 needs a full dovi_tool convert before tonemapping — often hours plus ~1× video size temp space on devices like CoreELEC. Use a desktop with Vulkan or leave this off to process them."

