msgstr "Download Pillow for preview cropping (into add-on site-packages). When the generator is enabled or HDR tone mapping is on, also offers ffmpeg/ffprobe and optional HDR extras (zscale/libplacebo, Vulkan loader on Windows, dovi_tool). Batch Run installs generator ffmpeg separately when generating sidecars."

